thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Robin Bayes

author: Robin Bayes
title: Robin Bayes
text: We love the Titan fluid and have been using it for five years now. The shipping is always fast and customer service is always friendly. The website is difficult to use on an iPad but from a desktop there are no problems whatsoever. We trust and enjoy the quality of these products. Plus, who doesn't love getting emailed coupon codes?
